headline: Maggie Kiselick,  Brendan Milnamow
abstract: The couple met in October 2016 through the League, a dating app.
lead_paragraph: Margaret Mae Kiselick and Brendan McCormick Milnamow were married Dec. 31 at the Roundhouse, a hotel in Beacon, N.Y. Claire Papp, a friend of the couple who was ordained through American Marriage Ministries, officiated.
